author: HBO Max
description:
Go behind the scenes of Peacemaker with creator James Gunn, co-hosts Jennifer Holland (Emilia Harcourt) and Steve Agee (John Economos) in the official Peacemaker podcast. In this episode they break down Peacemaker Season 2, Episode 5 “Back to the Suture,” share insider stories, and unpack major character moments. 

Special guests Michael Rooker (Red St. Wild) and DC Studios Executive Galen Vaisman join the conversation with hilarious and heartfelt anecdotes from set, fresh details on the DCU, and exclusive behind-the-scenes secrets you won’t hear anywhere else. 

If you’re a fan of DC Studios, James Gunn, or simply love learning how your favorite DCU series is made, this is the podcast for you. 
 
Subscribe for weekly deep dives into Peacemaker Season 2 and the evolving DC Universe.
